  "body": "\nDeep linking points at an addressable part of a node rather than only at a whole page.\n\nIn [XanaNode](/node/xananode), stable fragment ids and tumbler addresses give those links protocol identity. A deep link can identify the source node, version, and fragment being discussed or transcluded.\n\nThat is the practical bridge between ordinary hyperlinks and the [provenance](/node/provenance)-preserving reuse imagined by Xanadu.\n",
